snippet.title: Finana Ryugu 【NIJISANJI EN】
snippet.description:
Hi! I’m Finana Ryugu! 
A mermaid who spends my time with the tropical fish in the sea of coral reefs.
I have a heart as clear and pure as the calm and beautiful sea.
